{
  "info": {
    "name": "AAURA Phase 1 - Auth & RBAC",
    "_postman_id": "d7cc5f59-80b5-4a6e-a2f6-cf47e7d1cc00",
    "description": "Phase 1 test flow: login each role, provision, verify /users/me.\n\nBefore testing:\n1) Create users in Supabase Auth (Authentication → Users → Add user).\n2) Fill emails/passwords in environment **AAURA Local Supabase**.\n3) npm run dev (backend) must be running for provision + /users/me.\n\nSuggested emails:\n- student2@student.aaup.edu\n- club.lead@student.aaup.edu\n- affairs@staff.aaup.edu\n- dean@aaup.edu\n- admin@aaup.edu",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "0 - Setup",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Backend - Health",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": "{{base_url}}/health"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "AI - Health (via backend)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": "{{base_url}}/ai/health"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "1 - Auth Login (run one per user)",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Auth - Login (Student 1)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Login OK', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "  const j = pm.response.json();",
                  "  if (j.access_token) pm.environment.set('student_access_token', j.access_token);",
                  "  if (j.user?.id) pm.environment.set('student_user_id', j.user.id);",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "apikey", "value": "{{supabase_anon_key}}" },
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"{{student_email}}\",\n  \"password\": \"{{student_password}}\"\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{supabase_auth_url}}/token?grant_type=password"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Auth - Login (Student 2)",
